app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2218-1989/9/5/86/s1: Table S1: Ethanol yield in the flask fermentation trials fermented with Saccharomyces cerevisiae EC1118 (S. c.) and T. delbrueckii UMY196 (T. d.); Table S2: Chemical parameters determined for the fermentation trial with must/cherry juice fermented with S. cerevisiae EC1118 (S. c.) and T. delbrueckii UMY196 (T. d.); Table S3: Chemical parameters determined for the fermentation trial with must/peach juice fermented with S. cerevisiae EC1118 (S. c.) and T. delbrueckii UMY196 (T. d.); Table S4: Chemical parameters determined for the fermentation trial with must/strawberry juice fermented with Saccharomyces cerevisiae EC1118 (S. c.) and T. delbrueckii UMY196 (T. d.).
